    dc:creator "Laamiri, Sayef" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Myxosporea (Cnidaria: Myxozoa) infecting the saddled seabream Oblada melanura (L. 1758) (Teleostei: Sparidae) and the painted comber Serranus scriba (L. 1758) (Teleostei: Serranidae) in Tunisia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.581309> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.581309>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Photomicrographs of Ceratomyxa sp. 2 from the gall bladder of Serranus scriba. (A – B) Fresh mature spores in sutural view. (C) Mature spore in lateral view with two pyriform polar capsules (pc) and two sporoplasmic nuclei (sn). (D – F) Mature spores in apical view. Scale bar = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/581309/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

